Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體已經送達了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我很想和克洛維斯說話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要盡快執行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}被奪走的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 為什麼會在這裡 是嫌疑犯吧  克洛維斯殿下那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師說是抓錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過肯定是因為有可疑之處才會被抓的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是恐怖分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學校至少會確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒有區別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能只是害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和他說說話就知道是怎麼樣的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的行動力過於旺盛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經七年沒用過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,"去屋頂說話"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事都是多虧了你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是你 如果不是為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是把欠你的還給你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在密封艙裡的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥時很混亂 我們失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你那邊 沒有她的消息嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎除了親衛隊以外誰也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於名字… 還是叫你魯魯修嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的我 在記錄中已經是死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修·蘭佩魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在用的是這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍事法庭那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有怎麼轉來這裡上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到魯魯修居然也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了搜查能夠順利進行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某人作了這樣的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那個人還說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,17歲的話就應該好好上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全都是克洛維斯皇兄畫的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是皇兄呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功引出了游擊隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,推測其根據地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時向上匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…  柯內莉婭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舊時代的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,達爾頓  就是在這裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[安德列·達爾頓 Andres Darlton]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種戰力差距 沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧  愚蠢的ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的布里塔尼亞混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來ZERO不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逐個掃蕩也真是沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就在這裡腐爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  娜娜莉  笑世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我有禮物要送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然… 平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 今晚能留下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀已經是這個學校的學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以隨時都可以見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還有軍隊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也不是說每天都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還打算繼續做軍人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我被調到技術部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不再那麼危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,技術部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好坐著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和七年前不同  今天我是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像變得穩重了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你則是變得爽快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是讓你在房間待著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在新宿遇到的布里塔尼亞軍人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的話 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是… 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出來  傑雷米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[吉爾伯特·G.P.·吉爾弗德 Gilbert G.P. Guilford]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於查清楚了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是排除了關於謀反的嫌疑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ORANGE君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你們純血派放走了ZERO的事實卻不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,官降三級
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有兩個選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼從一個初級機師重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼回鄉下去種ORANGE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在學校還是裝作不認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和名譽布里塔尼亞人是朋友什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄不好還會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是皇子這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你也是這樣  儘是只考慮別人的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得  很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我還會有說這句話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊 你昨天好像有點奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒在學生會露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界史考試沒考好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是這樣的說辭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然新聞還沒有報導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但"武士之血"已被柯內莉婭剿滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可是中部最大的組織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻在一瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說ZERO  我們再這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要等待時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我會聯繫你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個喜歡纏人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該和他們斷絕聯繫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[滾回…貧民區]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 吵到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼沒去學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 不知怎麼… 總覺得…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們班裡來了個轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是殺害克洛維斯殿下的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙多次惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簽收的是男子的名字 沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把假面藏在這裡面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和Geass不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西可是能成為鐵證的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  這個香味… 又是披薩?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在攢必勝客積分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有沒有變得軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[意指吃必勝客吃到虛胖哦~虛胖~]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說上臂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不准碰哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想會不會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀被人欺負了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事 是需要時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能想想其他辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住! 還給我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能被一隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被區區一隻貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能因為這麼白癡的事而暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有碰哦  嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼很重要的東西被貓叼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要的東西是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但肯定是非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 哥哥那種驚慌失措的慘叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修的很重要的東西究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情書?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尷尬的相片?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫情詩的小冊子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情詩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會在魯魯修之前搶回來給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在他之前!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這時候那些恐怖分子在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能展開包圍作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再加深她的疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 我就這樣說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻貓怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是那個假面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我忘掉  剛才看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是學生會會長米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貓!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在請立即去抓住在校內逃竄的貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,社團活動全部暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,協力的社團可以享受經費預算的優待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 抓住貓咪的人還將獲得超級幸運大獎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 學生會成員的吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會… 也就是說… 我的也算?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身為學生會成員的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐的櫻唇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會只吻下臉頰就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算臉頰也滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 可以指定位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會會員的話 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修也可以咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望是米蕾姐姐比較好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在這種情況下做百合宣言啦 (Coming-Out)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,論機動力的話 我們佔絕對優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快找木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[木天蓼：貓最喜歡的"草本興奮劑",逗貓專用]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持就是勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捉到貓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把它叼著的東西交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長… 只會多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然擅自把人當作獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說布里塔尼亞人啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害 難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當初不設定成病弱少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什麼打扮啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是關係到我們的吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 那隻貓有什麼特徵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想它的腳可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為腳步聲稍微有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻貓是這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悠閒的學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在明明還是服喪期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 這裡的大學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經和他們談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不用把Lancelot趕出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注: NUMBERS是對被佔領地人民的通稱,比如日本為11]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還說NUMBERS不行什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我們學生會的人抓到它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也能得到獎品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是說吻的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也要認真地露一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不准在校內飆車!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 我們的吻就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後方就拜託莎莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮打算對誰用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是對… 魯魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼會那樣想?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…這個嘛…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也來追貓咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  學生會會長說要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了別管啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貓就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,運動是我的強項啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上次小鳥逃掉的時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別扯陳年舊事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往的體力白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經追到了是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰找到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前明明更加個人主義的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也過於安心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 突然渾身脫力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托轉校生的福 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是上次那隻貓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 救了魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯啊 轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻貓 是不是叼著什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像戴著什麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不知道什麼時候就掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是有東西忘了 讓我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的『尷尬的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為終於可以抓住你的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯太愛裝帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你們兩個人是舊識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 和ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能否讓他加入學生會?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們學校規定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生一定要加入某個社團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是副會長的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就算是一事平息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位都把耳朵湊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,米蕾承諾過的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就由還是半個會員的我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將就下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 為了慶祝抓住貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是由新人請客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別趁機敲詐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莎莉 多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是學生會會長米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有請神聖布里塔尼亞帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第98代唯一皇帝陛下發言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人 是不平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生來就健行之人  美貌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父母貧困之人  病弱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出生  成長  才能  所有人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人就是為了被差別對待而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人類才會爭鬥  競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由此才產生了進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不平等並非惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平等才有惡處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高呼權利平等的EU怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[EU：Europe Union，假想的歐洲同盟]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任期只是導致了眾愚政治而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[任期制：同帝國繼承製相反]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追求平等均富的中華聯邦呢?  造就了一群懈怠的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我們布里塔尼亞並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爭鬥  競爭  一直持續著在進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進化? 真是個好詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有布里塔尼亞在前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向著未來在前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吾子克洛維斯之死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是布里塔尼亞在持續進化的最佳證明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,競爭  掠奪  獲取  支配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在此盡頭  有著未來!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:22:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,All Hail Britannia…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修的敵人…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,"否定"這個詞都顯得太溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個男人就是布里塔尼亞的象徵的話 我就摧毀他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在這條路上 還有皇姐柯內莉婭阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經擁有了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.49,0:24:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我隻身一人也能…
